 with tread<br\/><strong>Rear brakes:<\/strong> Opposed piston type cable brake disc 140 mm diameter<br\/><strong>Materials used: <\/strong>Magnesium Alloy, Steel, Rubber, PU, PP, TPR, Eco-leather<br\/><strong>Seat adjustment:<\/strong> Seat height: minimum 370 mm, maximum 415 mm<br\/><strong>Rear brakes adjustment:<\/strong> Yes<\/p>","page":"bentley-trike-assembly"}},"item_QMVwhR":{"type":"item","settings":{"icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"HOW TO ASSEMBLE","content":"<p>Setting up your Tech Balance Bike is quick and hassle-free. Each bike is designed for simple assembly, allowing you to get on the road in no time. Follow the video guide below in ensuring a secure and proper setup. All necessary tools are provided in the box for your convenience.<br\/><br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=JdqDELbR0Wk\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=JdqDELbR0Wk\">How to Assemble<\/a><\/p>","page":""}},"item_LLNwn9":{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"SPARE PARTS","content":"<p>Every journey deserves to be seamless. If any part of your Bentley Trike needs replacing, continue the experience by ordering an official Bentley spare part <a href=\"\/products\/bentley-trike-spare-parts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bentley Trike Spare Parts\">here<\/a>. <\/p>","page":""}},"item_H639BW":{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"WARRANTY","content":"<p>If you experience any issues with your Bentley Trike within the <strong>2-year warranty <\/strong>period, we’re here to ensure a seamless solution. Simply enter your details in the form below, and our team will assist you promptly.<\/p><p><em>Please note : Warranty coverage applies exclusively to purchases made directly from us. If purchased elsewhere, kindly reach out to the original retailer for assistance<\/em><\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["item_xPccUw","item_tVpzTf","item_QMVwhR","item_LLNwn9","item_H639BW"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"subheading":"","title":"The Perfect Transition","content":"<p>Balance Bikes by Posh Baby and Kids are perfect for children as young as 18 months old to transition from tricycles to bicycles. The pedal-less bikes do much more than help teach your children balance, they also provide years of fun as they glide further, and into more uneven terrain safely.<\/p>","button_text":"","button_url":"","text_position":"start","background":"","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","heading_color":"","heading_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","accordion_background":"","accordion_text_color":""}},"video_jdAKz9":{"type":"video","blocks":{"play_wiMKpx":{"type":"play","settings":{}},"heading_TT7nKU":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"","heading_tag":"h1"}}},"block_order":["play_wiMKpx","heading_TT7nKU"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"allow_transparent_header":false,"autoplay":true,"video_size":"auto","video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/QPlay_Balance_Bikes.mp4","external_video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","text_color":"#ffffff","overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":30}},"rich_text_xpUPF4":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"subheading_9LHF9G":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"text":"Engineered for Every Stage"}},"heading_AfYRb4":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"The luxury stroller that grows with your child","heading_tag":"h2","text_color":"","gradient":""}},"richtext_9j3RyK":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"content":"<p>An innovative design that can transform from stroller to tricycle —designed to grow with your child through six stages, from 12 months and beyond.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_9LHF9G","heading_AfYRb4","richtext_9j3RyK"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":true,"content_width":"small","text_position":"center","background":"","background_gradient":"","text_color":""}},"rich_text_8hAWQk":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"subheading_6qwNDh":{"type":"subheading","settin